channel.title: Touchy Walrus - Kash Fayyaz
channel.description:
Hi Guys,
This my second beat using Auxy Disco.
I'd like to think its my best house/dance beat to date.
Would love some feedback and thoughts on this tune as well some of the other instrumentals I've made on my soundcloud profile.
Here's the link to my new tune - [Touchy Walrus ](https://soundcloud.com/kash-fayyaz/touchy-walrus-house-electronic-dance-edm-instrumental)
Peace & Love!
Kash
